OL,4,C'caring' wife in Bilston
OL,6,FA husband has been jailed for life
OL,7,Fafter admitting to murdering his
OL,8,F'caring and devoted' wife in Bilston
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FMother of two Kamaljeet Mahey, 45,
OL,12,Fdied on 15 December last year after
OL,13,Fbeing stabbed at their home on Park
OL,14,FMeadow Avenue.
OL,16,FHer husband Rajveer Mahey, 50, was
OL,17,Farrested after officers received a
OL,18,Fcall from the ambulance service who
OL,19,Ffound her with multiple stab wounds.
