OL,6,FCCTV footage shows Kamaljeet and her
OL,7,Fhusband enter their garage and an
OL,8,Faltercation is heard.
OL,10,FWhen detectives interviewed Mahey, he
OL,11,Finitially denied murder claiming his
OL,12,Fwife fell onto a knife.
OL,14,FHe said they had gone into the garage
OL,15,Ftogether as he wanted to make sure she
OL,16,Fwas choosing the right vegetables for
OL,17,Fcooking.
