OL,3,CHusband jailed after murdering
OL,4,C'caring' wife in Bilston
OL,6,FOnce realising that his wife was
OL,7,Fseriously injured, instead of calling
OL,8,F999 he called a family member for
OL,9,Fassistance before travelling to his
OL,10,Fworkplace to tell his manager he
OL,11,Fwouldn't be in work that day.
OL,13,FAt a previous hearing at Wolverhampton
OL,14,FCrown Court last month, Mahey admitted
OL,15,Fto murdering Kamaljeet and has been
OL,16,Fsentenced to life with a minimum term
OL,17,Fof 16 years and eight months.
