OL,3,CHusband jailed after murdering
OL,4,C'caring' wife in Bilston
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jim Mahon said:
OL,7,F"This is an absolutely tragic case
OL,8,Fthat has left two children without a
OL,9,Fmother an father.
OL,11,F"Instead of calling the police, Mahey
OL,12,Ftravelled to his place of work to let
OL,13,Fthem know he wouldn't be in that day.
OL,15,F"My thoughts remain with Kamaljeet's
OL,16,Ffamily."
